{"tid":2264828,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加強言論管控》轉發境外消息 重判3年有期徒刑","createTime":"2020-10-31T03:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T12:36:55.000Z","uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fcbabc679e0355157f08128fc18f863194de0359","tid":2264828,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"散布境外政治訊息 陝西13網友遭判刑<br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/31/phpHAANFw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F31%2FphpHAANFw.jpg&h=08b892e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n維權網報導，中國大陸陝西省13名網友因為被控在即時通訊群組傳播境外政治訊息，攻擊政府、黨和國家領導人，9月被法院以「尋釁滋事罪」分別判處1年6個月至3年有期徒刑。（彭博資料照）<br />\n<br />\n2020/10/31 11:13<br />\n〔中央社〕維權網報導，<span class=\"red\">中國大陸陝西省13名網友因為被控在即時通訊群組傳播境外政治訊息，攻擊政府、黨和國家領導人，9月被法院以「尋釁滋事罪」分別判處1年6個月至3年有期徒刑。</span><br />\n<br />\n其中，為首的陝西網友陳鷹軍開庭前拒絕公設律師為他辯護，表示要自己辯護；他<span class=\"red\">後來在庭審中只「高喊口號」，不做辯護，結果被判最重的3年有期徒刑。</span><br />\n<br />\n報導引述中國裁判文書網23日發布的判決書指出，陝西咸陽網友陳鷹軍、王興傑等13人因在QQ群傳播涉及政治的內容於2019年4月29日被捕，2020年9月被咸陽市秦都區法院以尋釁滋事罪分別判處1年6個月至3年有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n據判決書，咸陽市秦都區檢察院指控：2018至2019年期間，雷姓網友透過翻牆軟體瀏覽境外網站，將境外涉政虛假謠言（包括文字、圖片、影片）透過自己創建的多個QQ群進行轉發，又透過私聊發送給第二層級的被告陳鷹軍等8人，他們按照雷姓網友要求，轉發、散布到更多QQ群；被告李泰營等5名第三層級人員再次將虛假訊息繼續向更多的QQ群擴散傳播。<br />\n<br />\n咸陽市秦都區檢察院指控，以上被告為「發洩情緒」，在網路上「起哄鬧事」，散布虛假訊息，「攻擊政府、黨和國家領導人」，破壞社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n判決書還稱，<span class=\"red\">該組織的雷姓首腦人物已經死亡，「不清楚死因是否與本案有關」。</span><br />\n<br />\n被判刑的13名陝西咸陽網友分別是：陳鷹軍、王興傑、盧向輝、劉薌、周昱、朱遠亮、李好軒、徐海波、李泰營、周福評、潘建、廖煥華、武剛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3337564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3337564&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdndC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=79dc7e90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3337564&h=cb15a85e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3337564</a>"},{"pid":"b83800b5ec32ad9bb9762358d3b5cf23d0a58d88","tid":2264828,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1315d3497f240492c63fd78a8a963b2dfb9246f8","tid":2264828,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b83800b5ec32ad9bb9762358d3b5cf23d0a58d88","tid":2264828,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:33:18.000Z","msg":"不要用中國的軟體"},{"pid":"fff3415e4deed8f4c046062cd4631fb12e592f68","tid":2264828,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1315d3497f240492c63fd78a8a963b2dfb9246f8","tid":2264828,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b83800b5ec32ad9bb9762358d3b5cf23d0a58d88","tid":2264828,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T03:33:18.000Z","msg":"不要用中國的軟體"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10